Late Night with Jimmy Fallon - June 1, 2009

Tonight's lead-in is Conan's debut on The Tonight Show.
Slow Jam News with the Roots on the under-stimulated California economy
Episode 4 of 7th Floor West, a parody of The Hills
Guests: Oscar-nominated actress Anne Hathaway (smokin' hot in a skin-tight red dress), SNL regular Will Forte (MacGruber!), star Vegas chef Mario Batali, and actor Jon Favreau with his Iron Man hand (via web-chat).
